text: Lucas Dario Moscariello (born 19 February 1992) is an Argentine handball player for BM Ciudad Encantada and the Argentine national team.EHF profile2019 World Men's Handball Championship roster He participated at the 2017 World Men's Handball Championship.2017 World Championship roster ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male handball players Category:Liga ASOBAL players Category:Expatriate handball players Category:Argentine expatriate sportspeople in Spain Category:South American Games silver medalists for Argentina Category:South American Games medalists in handball Category:Sportspeople from Buenos Aires Category:Competitors at the 2018 South American Games Category:Handball players at the 2019 Pan American Games Category:Pan American Games medalists in handball Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Argentina
